OL,3,CCrews called to fire at Cwm Coke Works
OL,4,Csite
OL,6,FEmergency crews have tackled a fire
OL,7,Fthat broke out at the site of the Cwm
OL,8,FCoke Works site in Beddau.
OL,10,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,11,Fwere first alerted to the incident
OL,12,Fjust before 6pm on Saturday evening.
OL,14,FThey attended the scene with two pumps
OL,15,Fand one rescue tender. The fire was
OL,16,Fquickly brought under control and
OL,17,Fthere were no reports of injuries.
OL,19,FThe coke works and the colliery
OL,20,Femployed nearly 1,500 people at its
OL,21,Fheight.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/2
