OL,3,CCrews called to fire at Cwm Coke Works
OL,4,Csite
OL,6,FThe colliery was closed in 1986 and
OL,7,Fthe coke works was shut in 2002.
OL,9,FIn 2023 plans were approved to
OL,10,Fdemolish and remediate the site in
OL,11,FBeddau, so future development can take
OL,12,Fplace.
